You\\\\'ll be a genuine, motivated and professional person with a hands on approach in overseeing the Housekeeping operation.
Ideally, you\\\\'ll have the following qualifications and experience we\\\\'re looking for:
Proven pre-opening and operational experience in the same position in luxury hotel
Strong leadership and management skills
Detail oriented and extremely organized
Drive for results of high quality standards
Excellent analytical and problem-solving skills
Able to work under pressure in a fast pace environment
Further, as Executive Housekeeper, you will be responsible for
motivating your team.
You will be required to ensure that all staff within your department are adequately trained and developed in line with company policy.
You will actively guide and lead the team to ensure a high level of performance and service delivery.
Desired Candidate Profile
Ideally you will have 3 years of experience in a managerial role with relevant school/college qualifications. You will have experience in a similar role, have the ability to communicate at all levels and will be passionate about developing your career.
